{"type": "article", "id": 26915, "title": "靠一块地毯让房间变个氛围，这 3 个品牌就能帮忙", "description": "我们最喜欢 coldpicnic，你呢？", "date": "2016-05-17T06:46:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13377, "name": "纺织"}, {"id": 9835, "name": "地毯"}, {"id": 27720, "name": "alexkeha"}, {"id": 27721, "name": "hannahwaldron"}, {"id": 27722, "name": "coldpicnic"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 172, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185932mSL5rs1qRucOxl3b.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Instagram 从来就不只是用来凑热闹的地方，你总能在这里找到有两把刷子的各路高手。</p>\n<p class=\"\">之前，我们就介绍过在 Instagram 上晒厨艺（当然也有可能只是炫耀食物拍摄技术），结果晒出了一本美食书籍的账号。当然，你还能在 Instagram 找到一些艺术家踪迹。他们倒不是借了这里的热闹又来了个“点石成金”，而是把风格的确做得栩栩如生。</p>\n<p class=\"\">比如，纺织艺术就像是一种新生的媒介形式，可以把画家、插画家和设计师的技术和灵感都集于一身。下面这三个账号都是以纺织艺术为基础，专营地毯的工作室，分别来自纽约、伦敦和阿根廷，风格也大相径庭，但又自成一派，颇有些趣味。</p>\n<h2>1.<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/coldpicnic/\">coldpicnic </a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185917WVen8dylzmGpDC9Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99492386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185918lLNRvY73ZyX2MOAq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00343053\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185918DA9ieZfR5xOpjBNX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95719178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071859190pXVuRqbszKZmlSJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95704467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071859194PTKQBWVZrqtnMhF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95051195\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185920CaxkL5bUgsIpKTuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95213675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071859209aBWkGHe1TsmS5KP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38709677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">coldpicnic 是一个来自纽约布鲁克林的工作室，成立于 2010 年，主要擅长清新淡雅的小清新地毯。最著名的设计就是胸部简笔画地毯，这个元素一直贯穿在它的  Instagram 上。除此之外，就是用色温比较低的色块和线条做的简笔画一样的设计，说是灵感取自 1970 年代的美国电影风格。<br></p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hannah.waldron/\">2.hannahwaldron</a></h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185921qQR73tPrTFpK2odi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62092624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185921AyRPOKa7ig8sV9F5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93996569\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071859229x07Ihdwb1tR2aVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95051195\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185923GJXbVxQzc9NweT1v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95221843\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071859233yFshnIRqZtHTfxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93791946\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071859248OUpcH5qsz3BG1jD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99072356\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185924ABSuaw4IqCXQ5Wmb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91860465\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718592549m0v8drUlkhMWOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185925mYyEZ4xpjkIh1aAP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39083558\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">与第一个 coldpicnic 的地毯风格比较起来，hannahwaldron 的织物风格颜色浓烈又大胆，就好像是有人在你面前跳狂欢的桑巴，不过空间又需要替换一下，不是在南美洲而是在非洲。</p>\n<p class=\"\">物如其名，hannahwaldron 所有的产品都是手工制作而成。<a href=\"http://www.hannahwaldron.co.uk/shop/\">店主的自我介绍说了：</a>“有时在外游历，也会带上织物上路，有时候创作就会受到所处环境的影响，而设计出来的东西就是独一无二的。”</p>\n<p class=\"\">hannahwaldron 不仅售卖地毯，也有椅垫，和丝巾。一些带有非洲风情图案的丝巾则是在日本制作完成，售价为 32 英镑 — 40 英镑之间。而椅垫的价格为 75 英镑，印刷品的价格在 10 英镑以下。</p>\n<h2>3.<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/alexkeha/\">alexkeha</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185925NQ7dOW0hzR6i2qaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85787671\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185927aCLeomFB8rT1G3OR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18736842\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185927NW0G89YZjcbH1xEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.19829424\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718592898kYc34xjTWVKbMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10615711\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185928oWgiFIK2R6LzTM9j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25369979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185929kUCMXHz1382i7vBc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185930GrZwbn763TMz9tyJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65009208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185930CsZjbOmUqA5tM8Hl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71846435\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071859314djLo2Mh9kXyB6fv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24145299\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185931SgwAYFTnamBDQWvq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74315068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185932uiRNMA4oCzbec1aO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">不知道你有没有注意到，比利时品牌 Dries Van Noten 2015 年春秋季走秀的地毯格外迷人。这块名为 pastizal DVN 的地毯有 48 米长，像从油画中野蛮生长出来的野草，出自阿根廷的地毯艺术家 Alexandra Kehayoglou 之手，用了 16 天时间完成。同样，她也把兴致勃勃地把作品和创作过程放到了  Instagram 上。</p>\n<p class=\"\">“自然，以及如何将自然嫁接到艺术领域一直是我的初衷。” <a href=\"http://www.alexkeha.com/index.php?/refugios/press/\">Alexandra Kehayoglou 说，</a>“我是个环保主义者，我的草地地毯可以用来装饰屋子，同样也可以提醒人们要爱护环境。”</p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">题图和文内图来自：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hannah.waldron/\">hannahwaldron @ Instagram</a>、<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/coldpicnic/\">coldpicnic @ Instagram</a>、<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/alexkeha/\">alexkeha @ Instagram</a>。</p>\n\n\n"}